OL,6,FAmanda Wilkinson, Director of
OL,7,FUniversities Wales, said that the
OL,8,Findustries "that will drive our
OL,9,Feconomic growth in the decades to
OL,10,Fcome" rely heavily on graduates.
OL,12,FShe continued: "But it's not just our
OL,13,Feconomy and public services but also
OL,14,Ffor the people who would benefit from
OL,15,Fthe transformative experience of
OL,16,Fhigher education.
