OL,6,FMs Wilkinson said that Universities
OL,7,FWales will "continue to work" with
OL,8,FWelsh Government and Medr, Wales's
OL,9,FCommission for Tertiary Education and
OL,10,FResearch, to raise concerns and make
OL,11,Fthe case for participation to be a key
OL,12,Fpriority.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government said it is
OL,15,F"focused" on understanding what it can
OL,16,Fdo to "further increase participation."
