OL,3,C'Worrying' drop in university
OL,4,Capplications from 18-year-olds in Wales
OL,6,FWales has also seen a stark decrease
OL,7,Fin the proportion of those from
OL,8,Fdeprived areas applying to go to
OL,9,Funiversity, with 18-year-olds from the
OL,10,Fmost deprived areas in Wales the least
OL,11,Flikely to apply to university.
OL,13,FMs Wilkinson added: "Elsewhere in the
OL,14,Fdata, it is reassuring to see Wales
OL,15,Fcontinue to be a popular destination
OL,16,Ffor students, with Welsh universities
OL,17,Fseeing the biggest increase in
OL,18,Fapplications in the UK.
