OL,11,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said
OL,12,Fthey are "aware of the decrease in the
OL,13,Fnumber of 18-year-olds in Wales
OL,14,Fapplying to university" and continues
OL,15,Fto be "focused on understanding what
OL,16,Fwe can do to further increase
OL,17,Fparticipation."
